OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is set to face MPs in
OL,7,Fparliament as he seeks to explain how
OL,8,Fhe was not aware Peter Mandelson had
OL,9,Ffailed his security vetting before
OL,10,Ftaking up his post as the UK's
OL,11,Fambassador to Washington.
OL,13,FThe PM's statement, expected to be
OL,14,Fmade in the Commons this afternoon,
OL,15,Fcomes against a backdrop of calls for
OL,16,Fhis resignation, and claims he has
OL,17,Fmisled parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FStarmer has insisted he is "furious"
OL,7,Fno Foreign Office official told him
OL,8,Fthey had granted Mandelson security
OL,9,Fclearance despite him failing vetting
OL,10,F- a fact the department's top civil
OL,11,Fservant, Sir Olly Robbins, lost his
OL,12,Fjob over.
OL,14,FAddressing this last week, the PM
OL,15,Fsaid: "The fact that I wasn't told
OL,16,Fthat Peter Mandelson had failed his
OL,17,Fsecurity vetting when he was appointed
OL,18,Fis astonishing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,F"The fact that I wasn't told when I
OL,7,Fsaid to parliament that due process
OL,8,Fhad been followed is unforgivable, and
OL,9,Fthat's why I intend to set out in
OL,10,FParliament on Monday the facts behind
OL,11,Fthat, so there's full transparency in
OL,12,Frelation to it.
OL,14,F"But am I furious that I wasn't told?
OL,15,FYes, I am. Am I furious that other
OL,16,Fministers weren't told? Yes, I am. I
OL,17,Fshould have been told, and I wasn't
OL,18,Ftold."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FRobbins is expected to give his own
OL,7,Faccount of events to MPs when he
OL,8,Fappears in front of the Foreign
OL,9,FAffairs Select Committee on Tuesday.
OL,11,FAllies of Robbins have claimed the law
OL,12,Fprevents civil servants from sharing
OL,13,Fthe results of vetting with ministers,
OL,14,Fand that civil servants are there to
OL,15,Fenact the will of the government, with
OL,16,Fthe prime minister making clear he
OL,17,Fwanted to make the political
OL,18,Fappointment of Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FThis defence lies in the
OL,7,FConstitutional Reform and Governance
OL,8,FAct (Crag) 2010, which puts into law
OL,9,Fthat security vetting decisions lie
OL,10,Fwith civil servants, not ministers.
OL,12,FThose supporting Robbins' side in the
OL,13,Frow say ministers are not
OL,14,Fautomatically told of security vetting
OL,15,Foutcomes, and there is no legal duty
OL,16,Ffor them to be told.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FA statement issued by No 10 on Sunday
OL,7,Fsaid that although this is the case,
OL,8,Fthere was nothing in the law to
OL,9,Fprevent ministers from being told,
OL,10,Fespecially once it was clear Starmer
OL,11,Fhad told MPs due process had been
OL,12,Ffollowed.
OL,14,F"There is nothing in the guidance
OL,15,Fwhich prevented information being
OL,16,Fshared in this scenario, in a
OL,17,Fproportionate and necessary way and
OL,18,Fsubject to the appropriate procedural
OL,19,Fsteps," the statement on the Crag Act
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FWhile there are "legal obligations"
OL,7,Funder data protection rules, "no law
OL,8,Fprevents civil servants ` while
OL,9,Fcontinuing to protect such sensitive
OL,10,Fpersonal information ` from sensibly
OL,11,Fflagging UK Security Vetting
OL,12,Frecommendations or high-level risks
OL,13,Fand mitigations".
OL,15,FUKSV's privacy notice sets out there
OL,16,Fare "limited circumstances in which
OL,17,Frelevant vetting information can be
OL,18,Fshared" if "a security risk has been
OL,19,Fidentified".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
