PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMany, including opposition leader Kemi
OL,12,FBadenoch, have cast doubt on the prime
OL,13,Fminister's claims that he was kept in
OL,14,Fthe dark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FIn a letter to Starmer, Badenoch said:
OL,7,F"As an experienced barrister, you will
OL,8,Fknow the importance of telling the
OL,9,Ftruth, but you will also know that
OL,10,Fmany people think you have been at
OL,11,Fbest recklessly negligent and at worst
OL,12,Fdishonest about this whole affair.
OL,14,F"You have failed to answer very simple
OL,15,Fquestions about what you did and what
OL,16,Fyou knew. This is contemptuous of
OL,17,Fparliament, discourteous to the House,
OL,18,Fand against the fundamental
OL,19,Frequirement set out in your own
OL,20,FMinisterial Code."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FShe continued: "This has been a tawdry
OL,7,Fand shaming affair for you and your
OL,8,Fparty, and for this country.
OL,10,F"Not only have you damaged our
OL,11,Frelationship with the United States
OL,12,Fand insulted the victims of the
OL,13,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein, but you
OL,14,Fhave also undermined our national
OL,15,Fsecurity by giving the highest
OL,16,Fdiplomatic post to an individual that
OL,17,Fthe security services found to be of
OL,18,F'high concern'".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FBadenoch is joined by leaders from
OL,7,Facross the UK's political spectrum in
OL,8,Fcalling for Starmer to resign.
OL,10,FOn Sunday, Reform UK's Treasury
OL,11,Fspokesperson Robert Jenrick said he
OL,12,F"should be gone", while Lib Dem leader
OL,13,FSir Ed Davey said if he is found to
OL,14,Fhave misled parliament, he should
OL,15,Fresign.
OL,17,FThe Greens' leader Zack Polanski said
OL,18,Fon Friday, "there is on way today
OL,19,Fshould end" without Starmer's
OL,20,Fresignation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,7,Fhas accused the prime minister of
OL,8,Fbecoming "distracted from his day job
OL,9,Fand failing those he serves", whilst
OL,10,Fthe SNP's leader in Westminster
OL,11,FStephen Flynn has also called for
OL,12,FStarmer's head.
OL,14,FIn an effort to support its position,
OL,15,FNo 10 released the minutes of a
OL,16,Fmeeting which took place last Tuesday
OL,17,Fbetween the prime minister and top
OL,18,Fcivil servants Antonia Romeo and Cat
OL,19,FLittle.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FThese minutes claim Cat Little learnt
OL,7,FMandelson had not passed his security
OL,8,Fvetting in a review of documents ahead
OL,9,Fof their release in the files.
OL,11,FThe minutes read: "On reviewing the
OL,12,Ffile, she (Cat Little) had therefore
OL,13,Flearned that the recommendation from
OL,14,Fthe vetting officer had been that DV
OL,15,Fshould not be granted to Peter
OL,16,FMandelson.
OL,26,@tD@KpmtD@Vpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,F"There is some discretion for
OL,7,Fdepartments to proceed with clearance,
OL,8,Fand the FCDO had exercised it in this
OL,9,Fcase, granting Mandelson vetting
OL,10,Fclearance."
OL,12,F"The PM was not aware of any of this
OL,13,Fbefore the meeting, including that it
OL,14,Fwas even possible to grant clearance
OL,15,Fagainst the advice of UKSV."
OL,17,FLast week, Chief Secretary to the
OL,18,FPrime Minister, Darren Jones said he
OL,19,Fhad put an end to this power as soon
OL,20,Fas it was realised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,FA Cabinet Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"As part of the government's
OL,8,Fcommitment to comply fully with the
OL,9,FHumble Address, the permanent
OL,10,Fsecretary at the Cabinet Office
OL,11,Frequested the vetting summary document.
OL,13,F"Once she received this document, the
OL,14,FCabinet Office immediately undertook a
OL,15,Fseries of expedited checks in order to
OL,16,Fbe in a sound position to share the
OL,17,Fdocument, or the fact of it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,F"This included detailed legal advice
OL,7,Fon what information could be shared
OL,8,Ffurther in the context of the Humble
OL,9,FAddress, including from the First
OL,10,FTreasury Counsel; consideration of
OL,11,Fwhether sharing the information would
OL,12,Fprejudice criminal proceedings; and
OL,13,Fseeking information from the Foreign
OL,14,FOffice about the process they had
OL,15,Ffollowed which led to Peter Mandelson
OL,16,Fbeing given Developed Vetting
OL,17,Fclearance against the recommendation
OL,18,Fof UK Security Vetting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776777069
OL,3,CStarmer to address MPs over Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting decision
OL,6,F"As soon as these checks were
OL,7,Fconducted, the prime minister was
OL,8,Finformed."
OL,10,FFurther documents relating to
OL,11,FMandelson's appointment are expected
OL,12,Fto be released after the May elections.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
